SendmailAnalyzer (Perl Sendmail log analyser) continuously read your maillog
file to generate periodical HTML and graph reports. All reports are shown
throught a CGI web interface.

It reports all you ever wanted to know about email trafic on your network.
You can also use it in ISP environment with per domain report.

To use this tool you need an httpd daemon with Perl CGI support and some
libraries included in standard SlackWare distribution: libpng and libgd.
You also need some extra Perl modules that can be download from CPAN at
http://search.cpan.org/

	GD
	GD::Graph
	GD::TextUtil
	GD::Graph::bars3d;

After installing the package you must follow the instructions displayed at
the end.

